      <title>ICICI Prudential 预计印度债券收益率将走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/icici-prudential-sees-india-bond-yields-heading-lower-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ICICI Prudential Life Insurance 固定收益主管 Vidya Iyer 认为，外国机构投资者 (FII) 的流入加上强劲的国内需求将推动印度债券收益率下降。她在“彭博市场：亚洲”节目中与 Haslinda Amin 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/icici-prudential-sees-india-bond-yields-heading-lower-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 05:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
